    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Add some flare to your knife collection with the ASR Outdoor Damascus Etched Steel Hunting Knife! This full tang blade features a unique etched Damascus design, setting it apart from knives similar in size and style. It&#039;s constructed of durable stainless steel that wont rust, and features a cool wood grain handle. The overall length of this knife is 10&quot; and the blade itself is 4.5&quot;, a perfect size for keeping with your hunting gear, bag or backpack. It also comes with a thick nylon sheath that can be easily attached to a belt. This is a must-have addition to any hunter or knife enthusiast&#039;s collection!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 10 Inch Full Tang Hunting Knife Wooden Handle Damascus Etched Design</h2>\n  <p>Add some flare to your knife collection with the ASR Outdoor Damascus Etched Steel Hunting Knife!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>FULL TANG - Sturdy Blade Runs Full Length of Handle for Secure Grip &amp; Resistance</li>\n    <li>DAMASCUS DESIGN - Etched Blade Design Resembles Traditional Damascus Steel for Unique Look</li>\n    <li>ROBUST SIZE - Overall Length 10&quot;, 4.5&quot; Blade | Ideal Size for Hunting Gear, Bag or Backpack</li>\n    <li>NYLON SHEATH - Comes with Sturdy Sheath | Can Easily be Attached to Belt</li>\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Made of Stainless Steel that Wont Rust | Great for Hunting, Camping &amp; Outdoor Activities</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/fixed_knives/HBK201GD_huntingknife_main.jpg\" alt=\"Add some flare to your knife collection with the ASR Outdoor Damascus Etched Steel Hunting Knife\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRO10INHKGLD</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886044413</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 10 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This full tang blade features a unique etched Damascus design, setting it apart from knives similar in size and style. It&#039;s constructed of durable stainless steel that wont rust, and features a cool wood grain handle.</p>\n  <p>The overall length of this knife is 10&quot; and the blade itself is 4.5&quot;, a perfect size for keeping with your hunting gear, bag or backpack. It also comes with a thick nylon sheath that can be easily attached to a belt. This is a must-have addition to any hunter or knife enthusiast&#039;s collection!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
